title: Start
body:
Fishmonger: Ocean's greetings, young ones! Isn't the day magnificent?
[[Uh, sure? |choosefish]]
[[Totally!|choosefish]]
[[I almost fell into the water, so no!|choosefish]]

title: choosefish
body:
Fishmonger: This morning's bounty was a gift. I have some sea grouper, rock whitefish, and salmon.
[[Sea Grouper|chosefish]]
[[Rock Whitefish|chosefish]]
[[Salmon|chosefish]]

title: chosefish
body:
Fishmonger: There you go. I'm so glad you wanted some fish!
Renata: Why else would we come to a fish stand?
Fishmonger: I know! Tell that to the last lady who came by! She was more interested in Sindar Ruins.
Renata: Sindar Ruins?
Fishmonger: I didn't think they existed, but she seems convinced there's one right here in Kanakan.
[[Maybe she's right!|r1]]
[[Sounds fishy.|r2]]

title: r1
body:
Fishmonger: Perhaps. You're wise beyond your years, friend. May the day bless you like the ocean blesses the evening sky.
<<setHelpPrompt We can't go in there!>>

title: r2
body:
Fishmonger: Indeed, friend, indeed. May the day bless you like the ocean blesses the evening sky.
<<setHelpPrompt We can't go in there!>>
